# NBA2K Vault Cracker

A solver for the 4-digit vault code mini-game: guess a 4-digit code (digits 0–9,
repeats allowed) within 4 attempts, using red/yellow/green feedback per digit
(green = right digit, right spot; yellow = right digit, wrong spot; red = digit
not in the code at all).

## How it works

With 10,000 possible codes and only 4 guesses — the last of which can't use any
new feedback — the solver maximizes the Shannon entropy of each guess's outcome
against the full 10,000-code universe (not just the codes still possibly
correct). Spending early guesses as pure information-gathering "probes" splits
the remaining possibilities far more evenly than only guessing candidates that
could still be right, which roughly doubles the real-world success rate within
4 attempts (measured ~68-73% vs ~46%).

## Usage

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python3 -m vaultcracker.cli
